					<msContents>
						<summary>A series of names found on a group of rocks. The six first names (A, B, C, D, E, F) are found on the rock locally known as <foreign>noṇṭi vīrappaṉ kutiraitoṭṭi</foreign> ("the watering place of the horse of Noṇṭi Vīrappaṉ"), the seventh name (G) on a second rock nearby (G), the eighth name (H) on a third rock in the same place.</summary>
