      G reported in <bibl><ptr target="bib:ARIE1932-1933"/></bibl> (ARIE/1932-1933/B/1932-1933/106).
      H reported in <bibl><ptr target="bib:ARIE1932-1933"/></bibl> (ARIE/1932-1933/B/1932-1933/107).</p>
   
   <p>A, B, C, D, E, F<!--check!--> and G, H edited in <bibl><ptr target="bib:VenkatasubbaAyyar1943_01"/></bibl> (SII 12.23A.1-7), with visual documentation (of A, B, C, D, H). Text and summary in <bibl><ptr target="bib:Mahalingam1988_01"/></bibl> (IP 52.1-7). Edited here by Emmanuel Francis based on published visual documentation and photos (2011, by Emmanuel Francis).</p>  
   
